HOLyHammer is a machine learning for theorem proving framework.

Install Holyhammer:
  
  Run Holmake in src/holyhammer (done during the build)

Install external provers: Eprover(1.8 1.9 2.0, latest version should work too), 
  Z3 (4.0), Vampire (4.2.2)

  1) Download provers 
  - Eprover 2.0: 
      Source: http://wwwlehre.dhbw-stuttgart.de/~sschulz/E/E.html
        (eprover binary found in PROVER directory)
  - Z3 4.0 (not 4.4.0): 
      Binaries: http://isabelle.in.tum.de/components/
  - Vampire 4.2.2: 
      Linux binary: https://vprover.github.io/download.html
      Source: https://github.com/vprover/vampire 
        (produces vampire_rel_master_3993 in the top directory)
  2) Prover binaries with the appropriate version should be copied or linked
     in the directory src/holyhammer/provers.
     They should be respectively renamed to eprover, z3 and vampire.
  3) Make sure you have the permission to execute them (chmod +x)

Example:

  load "holyHammer"; open holyHammer;
  holyhammer ``1+1=2``;

Questions:

  If you have any question, you can send an email to 
  email@thibaultgauthier.fr

Commands for exporting standard library to TPTP formats:
  
  load "tttUnfold"; tttUnfold.load_sigobj ();
  val thyl = ancestry (current_theory ());
  load "hhExportTh1"; open hhExportTh1;
  th1_export_bushy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/th1_bushy") thyl;
  th1_export_chainy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/th1_chainy") thyl;
  load "hhExportTf1"; open hhExportTf1;
  tf1_export_bushy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/tf1_bushy") thyl;
  tf1_export_chainy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/tf1_chainy") thyl;
  load "hhExportFof"; open hhExportFof;
  fof_export_bushy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/fof_bushy") thyl;
  fof_export_chainy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/fof_chainy") thyl;
  load "hhExportTf0"; open hhExportTf0;
  tf0_export_bushy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/tf0_bushy") thyl;
  tf0_export_chainy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/tf0_chainy") thyl;
  val thyl = ancestry (current_theory ());
  th0_export_bushy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/th0_bushy") thyl;
  th0_export_chainy (HOLDIR ^ "/src/holyhammer/th0_chainy") thyl;
